Dependency Tree

  • org.apache.rat:apache-rat:jar:0.13
    Apache Creadur Rat::Command Line

    Description: This library provides upwards compatibility for projects, which are based on Apache Rat versions up to 0.5: Basically, it provides a JAR file, which is the combination of rat-core, rat-tasks, and its dependencies.

    URL: https://creadur.apache.org/rat/apache-rat/

    Project License: Apache License, Version 2

        URL: http://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-compress/
